<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77a61352-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s450rr–6"><num value="450rr–6">§ 450rr–6.</num><heading> Disclaimer of extraterritorial sovereignty</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">By enactment of sections 450rr to 450rr–6 of this title, the United States does not assert sovereignty, or sovereign or exclusive rights or jurisdiction over, or the ownership of, any marine areas or the R.M.S. Titanic.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77a61353-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/99/513/s8">Pub. L. 99–513, § 8</ref>, <date date="1986-10-21">Oct. 21, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/2084">100 Stat. 2084</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
